<< /DA (/CourierStd 10.00 Tf 0 g) /F 68 /FT /Tx /Ff 8388609 /MK << >> /P 45 0 R /Parent 30 0 R /Q 0 /Rect [ 18.0 443.259 39.172 468.771 ] /StructParent 12 /Subtype /Widget /T <feff0052006500610064004f006e006c00790033005f0046004c0044005b0030005d> /TU (Need More Help? If you have any questions, or need help completing the form: Bullet. Visit our website at w w w.s s ay.g o v for fast, simple, and secure online service. Bullet. Call us at 1-8 0 0-7 7 2-1 2 1 3, weekdays from 8:00 ay m to 7:00 pm. If you are deaf or hard of hearing, call T T Y 1-8 0 0-3 2 5-0 7 7 8. Please mention this letter when you call.) /Type /Annot >>
